I've been crying all morning so I'll try to keep this short. What started as rant (highlights cc: OG) I thought I'd regret later turned out to be exactly what I needed. It reminded me of.. shit me. And wish I could post everything but like, I'm overwhelmed and I don't deserve this love and thank you guys for being with me this past decade even when I disappeared for years. Thank you guys for always seeing me, knowing my heart & allowing my emotions not make me step out of character. Also thank you for never tryna change my character, esp rn when I was ready to, well they irrelevant now and life's great. 2024 we doing this art shit and I'm not taking the disrespect anymore bc those ppl are poop *future voice I'M JS BEING HONEST
